# VEHICLE::SET_VEHICLE_DOORS_LOCKED_FOR_ALL_TEAMS

## Summary
Locks the doors for all teams. Only used in the network game

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle
* **BOOL** locked
